		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well I'm not sure what this does but it looks like it's doing some kind of AM demodulation using 4xNAND gates as amplifiers by tying both inputs togethers and using feedback resistors for the frist 2 stages. What bothers me even more is that there is no feedback for the last 2 stages ! Normally the output should be constantly in a "staturated" state..

		

